title: #925toNoon AAF & Football Talkers/Micheletti in studio
description: PA presser to start, answering the tough questions as his late arrival for the 2nd consecutive Monday put the show in peril. Football/Wild/AAF talkers throughout, with Pat Micheletti in studio most of the final hour!
